Capital gain tax
\series default
: Consider selling a machine.
 The book value is the historical price, minus accumulated depreciation.
 Ccpital gain is the selling price minus book value.
 The liability on capital gain is the capital gain times the capital gain
 tax rate.
 Then, the CF from selling the machine is the capital gain, minus the tax.
